{"tid":2208371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中方︰堅決反對美國禁WeChat及TikTok交易","createTime":"2020-09-19T00:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T06:36:56.000Z","uid":18569,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"e01402b0301d5eeb85cfa971e6599db30994d64a","tid":2208371,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T00:28:13.000Z","msg":"中方︰堅決反對美國禁WeChat及TikTok交易<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部表示，當地星期日起，將在美國境內禁止與WeChat及TikTok的有關交易。在北京，商務部表示，美方的舉動嚴重損害有關企業的正當合法權益，擾亂正常的市場秩序，中方堅決反對。如果美方一意孤行，中方將採取必要措施，堅決維護中國企業的合法權益。商務部新聞發言人說，注意到美方以「國家安全」為由，禁止與移動應用程式WeChat和TikTok的有關交易，說美方在毫無證據的情況下，多次動用國家力量，以莫須有的理由，對兩間企業進行「圍獵」和打壓，嚴重擾亂企業的正常經營活動，損害國際投資者對美國投資環境的信心，破壞正常的國際經貿秩序。中方敦促美方摒棄霸淩行徑，立即停止錯誤做法，切實維護公平透明的國際規則和秩序。<br />\n<br />\n2020-09-19 08:22:48<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/437dYqD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F437dYqD.jpg&h=d2c572a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0fae546c45b282b4d5671fe730c10c78bcb01ae","tid":2208371,"uid":35087,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T00:29:03.000Z","msg":"民企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150829d80c03ed0e20366413951631ad3e513c89","tid":2208371,"uid":127435,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T00:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/au4jTZv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fau4jTZv.jpg&h=7b5fa31a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07a97715ae76c48e43d6394f7ad936a35ae9f6b4","tid":2208371,"uid":67468,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T00:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M49zHS7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM49zHS7.gif&h=d15853e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9002d7bf6551811ad8ce28ab43aded53cdf5f4e3","tid":2208371,"uid":67746,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T00:37:32.000Z","msg":"美國內政關你閪事咩<img src=\"/assets/fac